---
import SectionHeading from './SectionHeading.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <SectionHeading
    eyebrow="Profile"
    title="A structured, reliable approach to data work"
    lead="My strongest contribution is helping teams move from scattered operational data to reporting systems they can use confidently."
  />

  <div class="grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr]">
    <article class="reveal rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/6 p-7 backdrop-blur">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-cyan-300/80">Professional Summary</p>
      <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">I help organizations trust their data, not just look at it.</h3>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 text-slate-300">
        My background spans database design, SQL optimization, dashboard development, systems monitoring,
        data validation, and operational reporting. I work best where technical discipline matters and where
        business teams need accurate, usable information rather than noise.
      </p>
    </article>

    <div class="grid gap-5">
      <article class="reveal rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/6 p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-cyan-300/80">What defines my work</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
          <li>Dependable SQL and relational database work</li>
          <li>Power BI and Excel dashboards that surface the right trends</li>
          <li>Monitoring and validation that improve data accuracy</li>
          <li>Clear support for both technical teams and stakeholders</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="reveal rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/6 p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-cyan-300/80">Working style</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
          Detail-oriented, analytical, and comfortable in environments where accuracy, reporting discipline,
          and stakeholder communication all matter at the same time.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
